---
import BlockSection from "./BlockSection.astro";
import {Image} from 'astro:assets';
import avatarImage from '../assets/avatar.png';
---

<BlockSection id="about" header="About Me" backgroundColor="bg-blue-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
                <div class="bg-orange-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-400 border-4 border-black transform rotate-12 translate-x-2 -translate-y-2"></div>
                    <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden border-4 border-black">
                        <Image
                            src={avatarImage}
                            alt="Full Stack Developer"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-center font-bold mt-2">@logical-luke</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 space-y-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Journey</h2>
                    <p>My journey in tech began with curiosity about how things work. Over 10 years, I've mastered both frontend design and backend architecture, specializing in rapid MVP development. I tackle complex problems with enthusiasm, turning them into efficient applications that solve real-world problems.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-green-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Approach</h2>
                    <p>I believe in creating scalable, user-friendly solutions that drive business growth. Every project combines technical expertise with practical business understanding, focusing on:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li>✓ Clean, maintainable code architecture</li>
                        <li>✓ Performance-optimized solutions</li>
                        <li>✓ End-to-end project management</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-purple-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Beyond Code</h2>
                    <p>I'm a proud father and husband. I enjoy gaming and playing bass guitar. These diverse interests help maintain my creativity and problem-solving skills.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BlockSection>
